cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS 

This paper proposes a novel algorithm for quantization of neural networks using periodic functions as regularizers during training. The paper focuses on computer vision tasks and evaluates the proposed method on CIFAR-10 and ImageNet datasets. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, since the paper proposes a new algorithm, it may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
